<%- include('partials/head') %>
<div class="landing">
  <nav class="landing-nav">
    <div class="logo"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i> SecureVote</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline">Log In</a>
      <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="landing-hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Enterprise-Grade Encryption &amp; Security
      </div>
      <h1>Secure Voting for Schools &amp; Organizations</h1>
      <p>SecureVote provides a tamper-proof, auditable, and transparent voting platform built for student councils, clubs, and organizations. Every vote is encrypted, verified, and protected.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Register to Vote</a>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Admin Login</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">🔐</div>
      <h3>SHA-256 Vote Hashing</h3>
      <p>Every vote is cryptographically hashed with SHA-256, creating an immutable record that cannot be altered or forged.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
      <h3>Brute Force Protection</h3>
      <p>Accounts automatically lock after 5 failed attempts. Rate limiting prevents automated attacks on all endpoints.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">📊</div>
      <h3>Real-Time Analytics</h3>
      <p>Admins get live dashboards with voter turnout, participation rates, and comprehensive election statistics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">🧾</div>
      <h3>Vote Receipts</h3>
      <p>Each voter receives a unique cryptographic receipt code to independently verify their vote was recorded.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">📋</div>
      <h3>Full Audit Trail</h3>
      <p>Every action — logins, votes, admin changes — is logged with timestamps and user agents for complete accountability.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">✅</div>
      <h3>Identity Verification</h3>
      <p>Multi-step voter verification ensures only authorized, verified students and members can participate in elections.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">🏫</div>
      <h3>Built for Shared Networks</h3>
      <p>Works perfectly on school and company networks. Device fingerprinting and session tracking replace IP blocking — no false positives on shared Wi-Fi.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon">🔏</div>
      <h3>Device Fingerprinting</h3>
      <p>Advanced browser fingerprinting detects multi-account abuse without relying on IP addresses. One device, one vote.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
